Class MutableHandlerRegistry

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutableHandlerRegistryImpl

    @ThreadSafe
public abstract class MutableHandlerRegistry
extends HandlerRegistry
    Mutable implementation of HandlerRegistry. Used by server implementations that need to bind and unbind services that are exposed to remote clients.
